@startuml
title Token Exchange
actor User
participant IdP
participant Orchestrator
participant Gateway
participant Executor
User -> IdP: authenticate
IdP --> User: user token
User -> Orchestrator: submit request
Orchestrator -> Gateway: request with context
Gateway -> IdP: token exchange
IdP --> Gateway: scoped execution token
Gateway -> Executor: scoped agent token
Executor --> Gateway: agent output
@enduml
